@UPSHelp
 
Hello I have a shipment with you for days and no one has contacted me about the delivery so I want to know when you will arrive at my house because I started to get angry from the delay

@smoora_o My team would be glad to look in to the situation on your package. Could you please provide your tracking number, full address, and phone number in a direct message? Then we can take a look into what may be happening with your package.  Thanks - ^DC https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
